{
  "name": "Outbound LinkedIn Prospecting",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Outbound LinkedIn Prospecting & Reply Machine\n\n**Required Credentials**:\n- `APOLLO_API_KEY`: Sourcing prospects from the database.\n- `ZEROBOUNCE_API_KEY`: Verification token to validate emails.\n- `TAVILY_API_KEY`: API key to fetch recent company news.\n- `OPENAI_API_KEY`: Key for GPT-4o personalization and reply intent classification.\n- `UNIPILE_API_KEY`: Access token for automated LinkedIn invites.\n- `INSTANTLY_API_KEY`: Key to push enriched leads to email campaigns.\n\n**Environment Variables**:\n- Configure all API keys in your n8n global settings or map them in environment files.\n\n**Testing Protocol**:\n1. Execute the Cron-start path to verify Apollo data extraction and Split-in-Batches.\n2. Confirm ZeroBounce filters out invalid domains.\n3. Verify OpenAI writes a contextual intro line based on Tavily search results.\n4. Check that the Wait Governor adds a random 3-8 minute delay before sending the Unipile connection request to keep the LinkedIn profile safe.\n5. Test reply classification on the Gmail trigger path to confirm it correctly notifies Slack for interested responses.\n\n**Upsell Note**:\nNeed customized CRM logic or custom tools added? Hire **Automation & RevOps by Alfaz**: [whoisalfaz.me/contact/](https://whoisalfaz.me/contact/).",
        "height": 260,
        "width": 640
      },
      "id": "sticky-note-2",
      "name": "Workflow Instructions",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.sticky",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        100,
        -250
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": "0 8 * * 1"
      },
      "id": "cron-trigger",
      "name": "Cron Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.cron",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        100,
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "https://api.apollo.io/v1/mixed_people/search",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headersUi": {
          "parameter": [
            {
              "name": "X-Api-Key",
              "value": "={{ process.env.APOLLO_API_KEY || 'YOUR_API_KEY_HERE' }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ]
        },
        "sendBody": true,
        "bodyParametersUi": {
          "parameter": [
            {
              "name": "q_organization_domains",
              "value": "[]"
            },
            {
              "name": "page",
              "value": "1"
            },
            {
              "name": "per_page",
              "value": "20"
            },
            {
              "name": "person_titles",
              "value": "=[\"Founder\", \"CEO\", \"VP Sales\", \"Head of Operations\"]"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "apollo-search",
      "name": "Apollo Search",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4,
      "position": [
        350,
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "batchSize": 1,
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "split-batches",
      "name": "Split in Batches",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.splitInBatches",
      "typeVersion": 3,
      "position": [
        600,
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "=https://api.zerobounce.com/v2/validate?api_key={{ process.env.ZEROBOUNCE_API_KEY || 'YOUR_API_KEY_HERE' }}&email={{ encodeURIComponent($json.email) }}&ip_address=",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headersUi": {
          "parameter": [
            {
              "name": "Accept",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "zerobounce-verify",
      "name": "ZeroBounce Verify",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4,
      "position": [
        850,
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "caseSensitive": true,
            "leftValue": "",
            "typeValidation": "strict"
          },
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "cond-zerobounce",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.status }}",
              "comparison": "equals",
              "rightValue": "valid"
            }
          ],
          "combinator": "and"
        }
      },
      "id": "is-email-valid",
      "name": "Is Email Valid?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        1100,
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "https://api.tavily.com/search",
        "sendBody": true,
        "bodyParametersUi": {
          "parameter": [
            {
              "name": "api_key",
              "value": "={{ process.env.TAVILY_API_KEY || 'YOUR_API_KEY_HERE' }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "query",
              "value": "=Recent news and activity for company {{ $node[\"Split in Batches\"].json.organization?.name || 'Google' }}"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "tavily-search",
      "name": "Tavily Search",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4,
      "position": [
        1350,
        -100
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "chat",
        "chatModel": "gpt-4o",
        "messagesUi": {
          "messagesValues": [
            {
              "role": "system",
              "message": "You are a B2B cold email copywriter. Write a personalized first-line hook for [Prospect Name] at [Company Name]. Make it relevant to company news provided. Max 2 sentences, casual, professional, zero jargon."
            },
            {
              "role": "user",
              "message": "=Prospect Name: {{ $node[\"Split in Batches\"].json.first_name }} {{ $node[\"Split in Batches\"].json.last_name }}\nCompany Name: {{ $node[\"Split in Batches\"].json.organization?.name }}\nBio: {{ $node[\"Split in Batches\"].json.title }}\nCompany news context: {{ $json.results ? JSON.stringify($json.results) : 'No news found.' }}"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "openai-personalize",
      "name": "OpenAI Personalize",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.openAi",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        1600,
        -100
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "amount": "=Math.floor(Math.random() * 5) + 3",
        "unit": "minutes"
      },
      "id": "wait-governor",
      "name": "Wait Governor",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.wait",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        1850,
        -100
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "https://api.unipile.com/v1/linkedin/invitations",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headersUi": {
          "parameter": [
            {
              "name": "Authorization",
              "value": "=Bearer {{ process.env.UNIPILE_API_KEY || 'YOUR_API_KEY_HERE' }}"
            },
